Visual Problem Statement 1

Everyone wants to crack their first interview, Right!!

33% of Hiring Managers claim they know if they will hire someone within the first 90seconds of the interview.

Colaberry gives us a unique opportunity that helps all the students with their interview prep. Colaberry Instructor Mock Interview Critique dashboard is used to analyze mentors and mentees performance based on their survey score. It helps the colaberry team to see how well the mentors and mentees are doing during their interview Processes and ensure both are trending towards the right direction. So the process helps the students to crack the real life Interview for first attempt.




This is the article about mock interviews:

https://www.thebalancecareers.com/how-to-use-mock-interviews-to-practice-interviewing-2061626
